attachments.title: Snoop Dogg On Steelers OC Todd Haley: "Fire That Motherfucker"
attachments.text: Snoop Dogg, never one to be shy about his sports takes, has set his sights on Pittsburgh Steelers offensive coordinator Todd "The Todd" Haley. The Steelers lost to the Eagles tonight 31-21 and Snoop was not having any of it. He went on a motherfucking tirade about Haley and posted it to Instagram.
attachments.fallback: Deadspin: Snoop Dogg On Steelers OC Todd Haley: "Fire That Motherfucker"

text: Yeah. That game was so poor
All penalties, too slow on offense
Eagles looked pretty good, but it's easy to run the ball when LeBeau can't really blitz
Yeah I'm just not looking forward to opener with ravens
